    97	
    98	---
    99	
   100	## Phase 3 — Reference contracts package (`eden-contracts`)
   101	
   102	First real Python code: Pydantic bindings for the v0 JSON Schemas.
   103	Introduces the uv workspace + Python toolchain.
   104	
   105	**Units:**
   106	
   107	- **3a** — Pydantic models for the six v0 schemas. Root `pyproject.toml`
   108	  (uv workspace root) + `reference/packages/eden-contracts/pyproject.toml`
   109	  - `.python-version`. Ruff/pyright config ported from direvo.
